metadata.description: Under the Ax-1 historic mission to space, is the educational and revolutionary RAKIA mission. The founder of RAKIA - mission Specialist Eytan Stibbe, impact investor and philanthropist from Israel, is joining Axiom's epic NFT mint from space. Together with Forbes 30 under 30 digital artist Amit Shimoni, they’ve combined children's drawings from all over the world – to inspire the next generations of world-leaders with a strong message: “no dream is beyond reach”. The highest bid will get an honorary water well with their name on the plaque as part of House of Legends mission to provide access to clean water to communities around the world.
metadata.name: Wish Upon A Star by House of Legend
